{"tid":687970,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［歡迎熱烈討論］ 整甜品心得！！","createTime":"2018-06-02T17:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T07:23:58.000Z","uid":27971,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00755ff0d6d090b15d4cda56290e0ec2a294e466","tid":687970,"uid":27971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:46:54.000Z","msg":"我係女，平時鐘意整甜品，但整得好難食，次次整次次fail，次次fail次次整，想大家一齊討論下整野食心得。<br />\n我整過既甜品如下：<br />\nMacaron - 唔知點解整過起碼3-4次，得一次成功，但太甜，甜到牙痛，試過整綠茶味同朱古力味，但變左曲奇餅咁樣，有無高手分析下？會唔會係打蛋白打得太多定太少？<br />\nNew York Cheesecake - 呢個我成功既，但硬係覺得個味好平淡<br />\n千層蛋糕 - 想整類似Lady M咁既味，但整左出尼硬係好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n仲整過其他，但宜家未諗到，陣間再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856eaeced7ebb9800f4e255215c965d03f5b6faf","tid":687970,"uid":27971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00755ff0d6d090b15d4cda56290e0ec2a294e466","tid":687970,"uid":27971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:46:54.000Z","msg":"我係女，平時鐘意整甜品，但整得好難食，次次整次次fail，次次fail次次整，想大家一齊討論下整野食心得。<br />\n我整過既甜品如下：<br />\nMacaron - 唔知點解整過起碼3-4次，得一次成功，但太甜，甜到牙痛，試過整綠茶味同朱古力味，但變左曲奇餅咁樣，有無高手分析下？會唔會係打蛋白打得太多定太少？<br />\nNew York Cheesecake - 呢個我成功既，但硬係覺得個味好平淡<br />\n千層蛋糕 - 想整類似Lady M咁既味，但整左出尼硬係好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n仲整過其他，但宜家未諗到，陣間再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/015113_cfed4b41a5e950d1c05a4830e281c7d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F015113_cfed4b41a5e950d1c05a4830e281c7d4.png&h=2c985669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日整拿破倫蛋糕，好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/de